---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" currentPath="/">
  <!-- Hero Section: Swiss Modernist Layout -->
  <section
    class="relative min-h-[max(calc(100vh-160px),700px)] flex items-center px-12 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto overflow-hidden"
  >
    <!-- Background Geometric Soul -->
    <div
      class="absolute right-[-10%] top-[10%] w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full geometric-accent opacity-90 mix-blend-multiply filter blur-[2px] dark:opacity-30"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 w-full grid grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-end">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8">
        <span
          class="label-md text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary font-bold mb-6 block"
          >01 / MANIFESTO</span
        >
        <h1
          class="text-[5rem] md:text-[8rem] lg:text-[10rem] font-black leading-[0.85] tracking-[-0.05em] text-on-background mb-8"
        >
          LESS IS<br />MORE.
        </h1>
        <p
          class="max-w-md text-lg leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant font-medium"
        >
          A radical pursuit of objectivity and mathematical grid logic. We strip
          away the unnecessary to reveal the architectural soul of digital
          experiences.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- B&W Portrait with Sharp Edge -->
      <div
        class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-4 flex justify-end relative h-[500px]"
      >
        <div
          class="w-full h-full bg-surface-container-highest relative overflow-hidden group"
        >
          <img
            alt="Professional portrait"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale contrast-125 brightness-90"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCSHeegDGzzwqWlVo7xzxdySqkQ3JqU63lfN2C4SAaXLGeDXHvv_r2eCSM23rkq6ERhalMvQE187zKQJOH_1HPfdTmPi66VmTT-3m9Sysj9LZWLSAzaOH-3rnQQlrOBF0MQ5KMXY_t_Zn_FVqETU86n-azhrvIkpDf6OhE2XjwiWrBM0xLwCGp8qdl2fPFCIgdtTJ-ufJ_m0-6ozEVipaGTMDb05l71g9tzGkR4Y9z86OZbrx7YvF98eCkJjqgezMFemsBTm-b-WZ3P"
          />
          <!-- Technical Overlay -->
          <div
            class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-on-background text-surface text-[0.65rem] px-3 py-1 tracking-widest uppercase"
          >
            FOUNDER / ARCHITECT
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    class="bg-surface-container-highest py-32 px-12 border-y border-on-surface/5"
  >
    <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-4">
        <span
          class="label-md text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary font-bold mb-6 block"
          >02 / ETHOS</span
        >
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase mb-12">
          Core<br />Principles
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div
        class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16"
      >
        <!-- Principle 1: Fail Better -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3
            class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase border-b border-primary/20 pb-4"
          >
            Fail Better
          </h3>
          <blockquote
            class="text-xl italic font-serif text-on-surface-variant border-l-2 border-primary pl-6 py-2"
          >
            "Ever tried. Ever failed. No matter. Try again. Fail again. <span
              class="text-primary font-bold">Fail better.</span
            >"
            <footer
              class="text-sm font-sans uppercase tracking-widest mt-4 opacity-70"
            >
              — Samuel Beckett
            </footer>
          </blockquote>
          <p
            class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant font-medium"
          >
            In an iterative world, failure is the most reliable data point. We
            don't view setbacks as terminal; we view them as essential
            refinements. By leaning into the discomfort of the "broken" and
            analyzing the wreckage, we ensure that every version of our work is
            more resilient and sophisticated than the last.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Principle 2: Via Negativa -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3
            class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase border-b border-primary/20 pb-4"
          >
            Via Negativa
          </h3>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-primary uppercase">
            Excellence through Subtraction
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant font-medium"
          >
            Derived from the principle that we understand the world best by
            stripping away what is false or non-essential. In practice, this
            means focus is achieved not by adding features, but by removing the
            noise. We believe that the most robust systems are those that have
            been distilled to their core.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Principle 3: The Pale Blue Dot -->
        <div
          class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 space-y-6 pt-8 border-t border-on-surface/5"
        >
          <h3
            class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase border-b border-primary/20 pb-4"
          >
            The Pale Blue Dot
          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
            <p
              class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-primary uppercase"
            >
              Cosmic Perspective
            </p>
            <p
              class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant font-medium"
            >
              Inspired by Carl Sagan’s reflection on our "mote of dust suspended
              in a sunbeam." This perspective is a reminder of our shared
              responsibility and the scale of our impact. In the vastness of the
              universe, our efforts should be directed toward building things
              that matter—fostering connection and preserving our only home.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 03: SHOWCASE -->
  <section
    class="py-32 px-12 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto border-b border-on-surface/5"
  >
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end mb-16 gap-8"
      >
        <div>
          <span
            class="label-md text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary font-bold mb-6 block"
            >03 / SHOWCASE</span
          >
          <h2
            class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase leading-[0.9]"
          >
            Technical<br />Inventory
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p
          class="max-w-xs text-xs uppercase tracking-widest leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant opacity-70"
        >
          A curated selection of specialized instruments maintained for peak
          performance in high-stakes environments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-12">
        <!-- Snowboard Setup -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-6 space-y-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase">
              Alpine Kit_01
            </h3>
            <span class="h-[1px] flex-1 bg-on-surface/10"></span>
            <span class="text-[0.6rem] font-mono opacity-50"
              >SNOWBOARD_SETUP</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table
              class="w-full text-left text-[0.7rem] font-mono border-collapse"
            >
              <thead>
                <tr
                  class="border-b border-on-surface/20 uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface/60"
                >
                  <th class="py-3 pr-4">Component</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4">Model</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4">Status</th>
                  <th class="py-3 pl-4">Notes</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-on-surface/5">
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-bold">Snowboard</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4 text-primary">Korua Apollo 157</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4"
                    ><span
                      class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[0.6rem]"
                      >READY</span
                    ></td
                  >
                  <td class="py-4 pl-4 italic"
                    >Carving machine, +21°/+6° angles.</td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-bold">Bindings</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4">Rome Katana FASE</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4"
                    ><span
                      class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[0.6rem]"
                      >READY</span
                    ></td
                  >
                  <td class="py-4 pl-4 italic"
                    >Centering and strap adjustments complete.</td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-bold">Boots</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4">Nidecker Kita (Camo)</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4"
                    ><span
                      class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[0.6rem]"
                      >READY</span
                    ></td
                  >
                  <td class="py-4 pl-4 italic"
                    >Heat-molded, "Performance Fit" achieved.</td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-bold">Protection</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4">Demon Zero RF D3O</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4"
                    ><span
                      class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[0.6rem]"
                      >READY</span
                    ></td
                  >
                  <td class="py-4 pl-4 italic">No-limit mobility armor.</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Home Server -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-6 space-y-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase">
              Computation Unit_01
            </h3>
            <span class="h-[1px] flex-1 bg-on-surface/10"></span>
            <span class="text-[0.6rem] font-mono opacity-50">HOME_SERVER</span>
          </div>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table
              class="w-full text-left text-[0.7rem] font-mono border-collapse"
            >
              <thead>
                <tr
                  class="border-b border-on-surface/20 uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface/60"
                >
                  <th class="py-3 pr-4">Component</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4">Model & Key Details</th>
                  <th class="py-3 pl-4 text-right">Status</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-on-surface/5">
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-bold">Case</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4"
                    >Fractal Design Meshify 2 Lite (White)</td
                  >
                  <td class="py-4 pl-4 text-right"
                    ><span
                      class="bg-on-surface/10 text-on-surface px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[0.6rem] uppercase"
                      >Purchased</span
                    ></td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-bold">CPU</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4">AMD Ryzen 5 7600 (6-Core/12-Thread)</td>
                  <td class="py-4 pl-4 text-right"
                    ><span
                      class="bg-on-surface/10 text-on-surface px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[0.6rem] uppercase"
                      >Purchased</span
                    ></td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-bold">GPU</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4">RTX 4060 Ti 16GB (AI & Transcoding)</td>
                  <td class="py-4 pl-4 text-right"
                    ><span
                      class="bg-primary/20 text-primary px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[0.6rem] uppercase font-bold text-nowrap"
                      >FUTURE PLAN</span
                    ></td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-bold">RAM</td>
                  <td class="py-4 px-4">Corsair Vengeance 32GB 5200MHz</td>
                  <td class="py-4 pl-4 text-right"
                    ><span
                      class="bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[0.6rem] uppercase text-nowrap"
                      >NEGOTIATING</span
                    ></td
                  >
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
